videos.description: In his final home Duke game, Mike Krzyzewski walks out to a huge ovation from former players he coached as well as the fans.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Coach K gets rousing ovation from former players and fans) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Coach K gets rousing ovation from former players and fans

videos.description: UNC's Caleb Love passes to a driving Armando Bacot for a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot cruises in for easy UNC dunk) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bacot cruises in for easy UNC dunk

videos.description: UNC's R.J. Davis drives through two defenders and banks in the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (R.J. Davis splits defenders for UNC layup) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: R.J. Davis splits defenders for UNC layup

videos.description: UNC's Caleb Love tries to drop in a floater, but Duke's Theo John elevates for a big block.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Theo John gets up for massive Duke block) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Theo John gets up for massive Duke block

videos.description: Duke's Paolo Banchero can't drop in a layup, but puts back his own miss with a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Paolo Banchero gathers own miss for Duke dunk) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paolo Banchero gathers own miss for Duke dunk

videos.description: UNC's Brady Manek knocks down a smooth 3-pointer to push the Tar Heels out front.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UNC's Manek hits 3-pointer from top of the key) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: UNC's Manek hits 3-pointer from top of the key

videos.description: Duke's AJ Griffin knocks down a huge 3-pointer and everyone in Cameron Indoor Stadium erupts with excitement.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cameron Indoor Stadium erupts after Griffin's 3-pointer) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cameron Indoor Stadium erupts after Griffin's 3-pointer

videos.description: Duke's Jeremy Roach drives around a screen and gets the layup to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jeremy Roach gets friendly bounce on Duke layup) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jeremy Roach gets friendly bounce on Duke layup

videos.description: Duke's AJ Griffin comes up with a block and then Mark Williams throws down a dunk in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Griffin's block leads to Williams' dunk for Duke) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Griffin's block leads to Williams' dunk for Duke

videos.description: UNC's Leaky Black drives along the baseline for a reverse layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Leaky Black drops in smooth reverse for UNC) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leaky Black drops in smooth reverse for UNC

videos.description: Armando Bacot throws down a dunk to help UNC spoil Mike Krzyzewski's final home game at Cameron Indoor Stadium.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Bacot's dunk seals UNC's win in Coach K's final home game) 2022/03/05 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bacot's dunk seals UNC's win in Coach K's final home game

videos.description: Mike Krzyzewski gives praise to Duke's successful season despite the loss to UNC in his final home game at Cameron Indoor Stadium.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Interview (Coach K: 'Today was unacceptable but the season has been very acceptable') 2022/03/05

videos.headline: Coach K: 'Today was unacceptable but the season has been very acceptable'
